\subsection{Hallucination Mitigation and CoSC Efficacy}
We quantified the reliability of the agents by tracking the frequency of logical and syntactic errors. A critical outcome of our implementation is the agent's ability to maintain a \textbf{zero-adversary-impact} record across all 1,000 action decisions. Table \ref{tab:cosc_efficacy} details how the preventative CoSC gate managed reasoning failures.

